 class StaticPagesController < ApplicationController
  # thanks to http://www.imdb.com/character/ch0000002/quotes
  DANSKE_CITERE = { "Somehow I got the feeling that didn't work very much"=>"En eller anden måde fik jeg følelsen af, at virkede meget", "It's alright, I can see a lot better! Don't move!"=>"Det er okay, jeg kan se meget bedre! Flyt ikke!", "[as Lando is being dragged down by Sarlaac] Chewie, give me the gun! Don't move, Lando!"=>"[som Lando er ved at blive trukket af Sarlaac] Chewie, Giv mig pistolen! Ikke flytte, Lando!", "[to Chewie about the Ewoks] Well, short help is better than no help at all."=>"[til Chewie om Ewoks] Nå, er kort hjælp bedre end ingen hjælp overhovedet.", "A Jedi Knight? Jeez, I'm out of it for a little while, everyone gets delusions of grandeur!"=>"En Jedi Knight? Jeez, jeg er ud af det for en stund, alle får storhedsvanvid!", "Luke? Luke's crazy! He can't even take care of himself, much less rescue anybody."=>"Luke? Luke's crazy! Han kan ikke selv tage sig af sig selv, meget mindre redde nogen.", "Ch-Chewie! I can't see, pal. What's going on?"=>"CH-Chewie! Jeg kan ikke se, pal. Hvad sker der?", "Chewie? Chewie, is that you?"=>"Chewie? Chewie, er det dig?", "Just what I always wanted."=>"Bare hvad jeg altid ønskede.", "I have a really bad feeling about this."=>"Jeg har en rigtig dårlig fornemmelse om dette.", "Hurry up, will ya? Haven't got all day!"=>"Skynd dig, vil ya? Har ikke fået hele dagen!", "Try and get our weapons back."=>"Prøv og få vores våben tilbage.", "We need some fresh supplies too."=>"Vi har brug for nogle friske forsyninger også.", "Good. How far is it? Ask him."=>"God. Hvor langt er det? Spørge ham.", "Who are you?"=>"Hvem er du?", "Right?"=>"Ret?", "3PO. You tell that slimy piece of worm-ridden filth, he'll get no such pleasure from us."=>"3PO. du fortælle at slimet stykke af orm-redet skidt, han får ingen sådanne glæde fra os.", "*I* don't know. Fly casual."=>"* Jeg * ikke kender. Flyve casual.", "Now don't get jittery, Luke. There are a lot of command ships. Keep your distance, though, Chewie, but don't *look* like you're trying to keeping your distance."=>"Nu ikke få nervøs, Luke. Der er en masse kommando skibe. Holde din distance, selv, Chewie, men ikke * ser * som du forsøger at holde din distance.", "That bad, huh?"=>"Det dårlige, huh?", "How we doin'?"=>"Hvordan vi doin'?", "Together again, huh?"=>"Sammen igen, huh?", "Then we'll do it real quiet-like."=>"Derefter vil vi gøre det rigtige ro-lignende.", "On second thought, let's pass on that, huh?"=>"Ved nærmere eftertanke, lad os give videre, huh?", "Doesn't sound so bad."=>"Ikke lyd så slemt.", "Good, I hate long waits."=>"Godt, hader jeg lange ventetider.", "I love you."=>"Jeg elsker dig.", "Proper?"=>"Korrekt?", "Well, why don't you use your divine influence and get us out of this?"=>"Nå, hvorfor ikke du bruger din guddommelige indflydelse og få os ud af dette?", "You're going to die here, you know. Convenient."=>"Du vil dø her, kender du. Praktisk.", "I think my eyes are getting better. Instead of a big dark blur, I see a big light blur."=>"Jeg tror, mine øjne bliver bedre. I stedet for en stor mørk blur ser jeg en stor lys sløring.", "Hey, it's me."=>"Hey, er det mig.", "Chewie and I'll take care of this, you stay here."=>"Chewie og jeg vil tage sig af dette, du opholder dig her.", "[disguised as an Imperial] It's over, Commander. The rebels have been routed and they're fleeing into the woods. We need reinforcements to continue the pursuit."=>"[forklædt som en Imperial] Det er overstået, Commander. Oprørerne har været dirigeres og de flygter ind i skoven. Vi har brug for forstærkninger at fortsætte forfølgelsen.", "It's your imagination, kid. Come on. Let's keep a little optimism here."=>"Det er din fantasi, kid. Kom nu. Lad os holde lidt optimisme her.", "Wait, I know that laugh..."=>"Vent, jeg ved at grine...", "Hey, Luke, thanks. Thanks for coming after me. I owe you one."=>"Hey, Luke, tak. Tak for at komme efter mig. Jeg skylder dig en.", "Did you tell Luke? Is that who you could tell?"=>"Har du fortælle Luke? Er det, som du kunne fortælle?", "All right. I understand. Fine. When he comes back, I won't get in the way."=>"All right. Jeg forstår. Bøde. Når han kommer tilbage, vil ikke jeg komme i vejen.", "don't you?"=>"gør du ikke?", "You love him,"=>"Du elsker ham,", "I'm sure Luke wasn't on that thing when it blew."=>"Jeg er sikker på Luke var ikke på at ting når det blæste.", "Well, who says they didn't? Only I ain't crazy."=>"Nå, der siger de ikke? Kun jeg er ikke skør.", "Well, don't look at me, pal. I just said you were a fair pilot. I didn't know they were looking for somebody to *lead* this crazy attack."=>"Nå, ikke se på mig, kammerat. Jeg sagde bare, du var en fair pilot. Jeg vidste ikke de var på udkig efter nogen til at * føre * denne skøre angreb.", "Well, look at you! A General, huh?"=>"Nå, se på dig! En generel, huh?", "You're gonna die here, you know. Convenient."=>"Du vil dø her, kender du. Praktisk.", "[flying across the deserts of Tatooine] I think my eyes are getting better. Instead of a big dark blur, I see a big bright blur."=>"[flyver på tværs af ørkener i Tatooine] Jeg tror, mine øjne bliver bedre. I stedet for en stor mørk blur ser jeg en stor lyse sløring.", "Boba Fett? Boba Fett? Where?"=>"Boba Fett? Boba Fett? Hvor?", "[when a toolbox falls on his head] OOOOW!"=>"[når en værktøjskasse falder på hovedet] OOOOW!", "Deck officer! Deck officer!"=>"Dæk officer! Dæk officer!", "You could use a good kiss!"=>"Du kan bruge et godt kys!", "I could arrange that!"=>"Jeg kunne arrangere der!", "Am I? Then why are you following me afraid I was gonna leave without giving you a goodbye kiss?"=>"Jeg? Så hvorfor er du efter mig bange for jeg skulle til at forlade uden at give dig et farvel kys?", "A-ha! Come on!"=>"A-ha! Kom nu!", "No! That's not it. Come on."=>"Nej! Det er ikke det. Kom nu.", "Come on you want me to stay because of the way you feel about me."=>"Komme på du have mig til at bo på grund af den måde, du føler om mig.", "You probably don't."=>"Du sandsynligvis ikke.", "Well, what about YOU need?"=>"Nå, hvad med jer savn?", "We need?"=>"Vi har brug for?", "[C-3PO won't stop complaining] Either shut him up or shut him down!"=>"[C-3PO plejer stop klagende] Enten kæft ham eller lukke ham ned!", "What's going on... Buddy?"=>"Hvad sker der... Kammerat?", "This is no cave."=>"Dette er ingen cave.", "[after being tortured] I feel terrible."=>"[efter at være blevet tortureret] Jeg føler forfærdeligt.", "Then I'll see you in Hell!"=>"Så jeg vil se dig i helvede!", "There isn't enough life on this ice cube to fill a space cruiser. Sensors are placed. I'm going back."=>"Der er ikke nok liv på denne isterning at fylde en space cruiser. Sensorer er placeret. Jeg har tænkt mig tilbage.", "Loud and clear, kid. What's up?"=>"Højt og tydeligt, kid. Hvad sker der?", "I'm not going to argue with that."=>"Jeg har ikke tænkt mig at argumentere med, at.", "I'm sorry too."=>"Jeg beklager også.", "That's two you owe me junior."=>"Der er to du skylder mig junior.", "How ya feeling kid? You don't look so bad to me. You look strong enough to pull the ears off a gundark."=>"Hvordan ya følelse kid? Du ser ikke så slemt for mig. Du ser stærk nok til at trække ører off en gundark.", "OW! Chewie!"=>"OW! Chewie!", "Horizontal boosters. Alluvial dampers? Ow! That's not it, bring me the Hydrospanner. I don't know how we're going to get out of this one."=>"Vandrette boostere. Alluviale dæmpere? Ow! Det er ikke det, bringe mig i Hydrospanner. Jeg ved ikke, hvordan vi skal komme ud af denne ene.", "Thank you. Thank you very much."=>"Tak. Mange tak.", "Well, that was a long time ago, I'm sure he's forgotten about that."=>"Nå, det var lang tid siden, jeg er sikker på, han er glemt om der.", "We're in trouble!"=>"Vi er i knibe!", "I think we're in trouble."=>"Jeg tror, vi er i problemer.", "Oh, yeah? Watch this."=>"Åh ja? Se denne.", "[to C-3PO] Hurry up, goldenrod! Or you're gonna be a permanent resident!"=>"[til C-3PO] Skynd dig, Gyldenris! Eller du vil blive en permanent resident!", "No, no problem. Why?"=>"Nej, ingen problem. Hvorfor?", "I know."=>"Jeg ved.", "[as Chewie tries to fight off the imperials and free Han] No! Stop, Chewie, stop! Chewie! Chewie this won't help me! Hey! Save your strength. There'll be another time. The Princess. You have to take care of her. You hear me? Huh?"=>"[som Chewie forsøger at kæmpe mod imperials og gratis Han] Nej! Stop, Chewie, stop! Chewie! Chewie dette vil ikke hjælpe mig! Hej! Gem din styrke. Der vil være en anden gang. Prinsesse. Du er nødt til at tage sig af hende. Du høre mig? Huh?", "I'm not really interested in your opinion 3PO."=>"Jeg er ikke rigtig interesseret i din mening 3PO.", "No time to discuss this as a committee."=>"Ingen tid til at diskutere dette som et udvalg.", "Why not?"=>"Hvorfor ikke?", "YOUR ship? Hey, remember you lost her to me, fair and square."=>"DIT skib? Hey, kan du huske at du tabte hende til mig, fair og firkantet.", "Ah, repairs. I was hoping you could help me out."=>"Ah, reparationer. Jeg håbede, du kunne hjælpe mig.", "I'm nice men."=>"Jeg er dejlig mand.", "You like me because I'm a scoundrel. There aren't enough scoundrels in your life."=>"Du kan lide mig, fordi jeg er en slyngel. Der er ikke nok skurke i dit liv.", "You're trembling."=>"Du rystende.", "My hands are dirty, too. What are you afraid of?"=>"Mine hænder er beskidte, også. Hvad er du bange for?", "Stop what?"=>"Stop hvad?", "Scoundrel? Scoundrel? I like the sound of that."=>"Slyngel? Slyngel? Jeg kan lide lyden af der.", "I do, I really do. You could be a little nicer, though. Come on, admit it. Sometimes you think I'm all right."=>"Jeg gør, gør jeg virkelig. Du kunne være lidt pænere, selv. Kom nu, indrømme det. Sommetider tror du jeg er okay.", "Sure, Leia."=>"Sikker, Leia.", "Hey, Your Worship, I'm only trying to help."=>"Hey, din gudstjeneste, jeg kun forsøger at hjælpe.", "[also sarcastic] It might!"=>"[også sarkastisk] Det kan!", "Not entirely stable. I'm glad you're here to tell us these things. Chewie! Take the Professor in back and plug him into the hyperdrive!"=>"Ikke helt stabil. Jeg er glad for du er her for at fortælle os disse ting. Chewie! Tage professoren i ryggen og sætte ham i hyperdrive!", "They'd be crazy to follow us, wouldn't they?"=>"De ville være vanvittigt at følge os, ville de?", "Yeah, me too."=>"Ja, mig også.", "You said you wanted to be around when I made a mistake, well, this could be it, sweetheart."=>"Du sagde du ville være omkring når jeg lavede en fejl, godt, dette kunne være det, kæreste.", "[cutting open his dead Tauntaun and shoving Luke inside] This may smell bad, kid, but it'll keep you warm until I get the shelter up... Ugh. And I thought they smelled bad on the *outside*."=>"[skære åbne hans døde Tauntaun og shoving Luke inde] Dette kan lugte dårligt, kid, men det vil holde dig varm indtil jeg får ly... Uh. Og jeg troede, de lugtede grimt på de * udenfor *.", "Laugh it up, fuzzball."=>"Grine det op, fuzzball.", "That's a good story. I think you just can't bear to let a gorgeous guy like me out of your sight."=>"Det er en god historie. Jeg tror, du bare ikke kan bære for at lade en smukke fyr som mig ud af dit syn.", "Well Princess, it looks like you managed to keep me here a while longer."=>"Godt prinsesse, det ser ud til du har formået at holde mig her et stykke tid længere.", "I can arrange that. You could use a good kiss."=>"Jeg kan arrangere der. Du kan bruge et godt kys.", "Afraid I was gonna leave without giving you a goodbye kiss?"=>"Bange for jeg skulle til at forlade uden at give dig et farvel kys?", "It's not my fault."=>"Det er ikke min skyld.", "Sorry sweetheart. I haven't got time for anything else."=>"Undskyld kæreste. Jeg har ikke fået tid til noget andet.", "Don't get excited."=>"Ikke blive ophidset.", "Shh."=>"Shh.", "Never tell me the odds."=>"Aldrig fortælle mig odds.", "Who's scruffy-looking?"=>"Der scruffy udseende?", "I hate that guy."=>"Jeg hader at fyr.", "[Rey rushes by him into the Falcon's cockpit] Hey, where are you going?"=>"[Rey styrter af ham i den Falcon cockpit] Hey, hvor skal du hen?", "If Luke couldn't reach him, how could I?"=>"Hvis Luke ikke kunne nå ham, hvordan kunne jeg?", "We lost our son. Forever."=>"Vi mistede vores søn. For evigt.", "We both had to deal with it in our own way. I went back to the only thing I was ever any good at."=>"Vi begge måtte beskæftige sig med det på vores egen måde. Jeg gik tilbage til det eneste jeg var stadig god til.", "There's nothing more we could have done. There's too much Vader in him."=>"Der er ikke noget mere vi kunne have gjort. Der er for meget Vader i ham.", "Listen to me, will you? I know every time you... Every time you look at me you're reminded of him."=>"Lyt til mig, vil du? Jeg ved, hver gang du... Hver gang du ser på mig du er mindet om ham.", "Their shields have a fractional refresh rate. Keeps anything traveling slower than lightspeed from getting through."=>"Deres skjolde har en fraktioneret opdateringshastighed. Holder noget langsommere end lightspeed på rejse fra at komme igennem.", "If I told you, you wouldn't like it."=>"Hvis jeg fortalte dig, kan du ikke lide det.", "[looking at Chewie] We'll get you there."=>"[ser på Chewie] Vi skal nok få dig der.", "They're big and they're dangerous."=>"De er store, og de er farlige.", "I'm hauling Rathtars. Oh, great. It's the Guavian Death Gang. Must have tracked us from Nantoon."=>"Jeg indhaling Rathtars. Åh, fantastisk. Det er Guavian død bande. Skal have sporet os fra Nantoon.", "Oh, don't tell me a Rathtar's gotten loose."=>"Åh, ikke fortælle mig en Rathtar er kommet løs.", "What was the second time?"=>"Det var anden gang?", "Boys, you're both gonna get what I promised. Have I ever not delivered for you before?"=>"Drenge, du både gonna få hvad jeg lovede. Har jeg nogensinde ikke leveret til dig før?", "Tasu Leech. Good to see you."=>"Tasu Leech. Godt at se dig.", "I never made a deal with Kanjuklub!"=>"Jeg har aldrig lavet en aftale med Kanjuklub!", "[to BB-8] Move, ball."=>"[til BB-8] Flytte, bold.", "Finn, be careful with those. They're explosives."=>"Finn, være omhyggelig med dem. De er sprængstoffer.", "Any of it."=>"Noget af den.", "Relax, kid. She's run this watering hole for a thousand years. Maz is a bit of an acquired taste, so let me do the talking. And whatever you do, don't stare."=>"Slap af, kid. Hun har kørt dette vandhul i tusind år. MAZ er lidt af en erhvervet smag, så lad mig tale. Og uanset hvad du gør, ikke stirre.", "You think it was luck that Chewie and I found the Falcon? If we can find it on our scanners, the First Order's not far behind. Wanna get BB-8 to the Resistance? Maz Kanata's our best bet."=>"Du tror det var held at Chewie og jeg fundet Falcon? Hvis vi kan finde den på vores scannere,'s den første ordre ikke langt bagefter. ønsker at få BB-8 til modstanden? MAZ Kanata er vores bedste bud.", "I never ask that question 'till after I've done it."=>"Jeg stille aldrig spørgsmålet til efter jeg har gjort det.", "Watch the thrust. We're going out of here at lightspeed."=>"Se essensen. Vi kommer ud af her på lightspeed.", "Is there a garbage chute? Trash compactor?"=>"Er der et skrald sliske? Trash compactor?", "I'm trying to be helpful."=>"Jeg forsøger at være hjælpsom.", "Do what?"=>"Gøre hvad?", "Leia."=>"Leia.", "Hey! Some moof-milker put a compressor on the ignition line."=>"Hej! Nogle Nik-malkeren sætter en kompressor på linjen tænding.", "[to Chewbacca] Told you we should have double-checked the Western Reaches."=>"[til Chewbacca] Fortalte dig vi skal har dobbelt-tjekket Western når.", "Jakku? That junkyard?"=>"Jakku? Junkyard?", "Where'd you get this ship?"=>"Hvor ville du få dette skib?", "I like this thing."=>"Jeg kan lide denne ting.", "Hey, can I try that?"=>"Hey, kan jeg prøve det?", "And 'that thing' can understand you, too, so watch it."=>"Og at ting kan forstå dig, også, så se den.", "Oh, really? You're cold?"=>"Åh, virkelig? Er du kold?", "[to Finn] Bring it down. Bring it down."=>"[til Finn] Bringe det ned. Bringe det ned.", "Yes, I do. Every time."=>"Ja jeg gør. Hver gang.", "Same thing I always do. Talk my way out of it."=>"Samme ting jeg altid gør. Tale min vej ud af det.", "You hurt Chewie, you're gonna deal with me!"=>"Du ondt Chewie, du vil behandle mig!", "Listen, Big Deal. You got another problem. Women always figure out the truth. Always."=>"Hør, Big Deal. Du fik et andet problem. Kvinder finde altid ud af sandheden. Altid.", "Did you just call me Solo?"=>"Du bare kalde mig Solo?", "I'm thinking about it."=>"Jeg tænker på det.", "I wouldn't be nice to you. Doesn't pay much."=>"Jeg ville ikke være rart for dig. Ikke betale meget.", "Yeah. I knew him. I knew Luke."=>"Ja. Jeg kendte ham. Jeg vidste Lukas.", "My help?"=>"Min hjælp?", "That's why I did it. So you'd miss me."=>"Thats hvorfor jeg gjorde det. Så du ville savne mig.", "Chewie's working on the Falcon."=>"Chewies arbejde på Falcon.", "Hey, Maz."=>"Hey, Maz.", "[softly] Oh, boy."=>"[sagte] Oh, dreng.", "Yes. Anything."=>"Ja. Noget.", "No, it's not. Leave here with me. Come home. We miss you."=>"Nej, det er ikke. Forlade her hos mig. Kommer hjem. Vi savner dig.", "Snoke is using you for your power. When he gets what he wants, he'll crush you. You know it's true."=>"Snoke bruger du for din magt. Når han får, hvad han vil, vil han knuse dig. Du ved, det er sandt.", "That's what Snoke wants you to believe, but it's not true. My son is alive."=>"Det er, hvad Snoke ønsker du at tro, men det er ikke sandt. Min søn er i live.", "The face of my son."=>"Ansigt med min søn.", "Take off that mask. You don't need it."=>"Tag denne maske. Du behøver det.", "Kylo Ren: I've been waiting for this day for a long time."=>"Kylo Ren: Jeg har ventet på denne dag i lang tid.", "Ben!"=>"Ben!", "Okay. How do we blow it up? There's always a way to do that."=>"Okay. Hvordan vi blæse det? Der er altid en måde at gøre dette.", "No, new jacket."=>"Nej, ny jakke.", "You changed your hair."=>"Du har ændret dit hår.", "That's not how the Force works!"=>"Thats ikke hvordan kraften, der virker!", "People are counting on us. The galaxy is counting on us."=>"Folk regner os. Galaksen er regner med os.", "Sanitation? Then how do you know how to disable the shields?"=>"Sanitet? Så hvordan kan du vide hvordan man deaktivere skjolde?", "What was your job when you were based here?"=>"Hvad var dit job, når du var baseret her?", "Fourteen."=>"14.", "Twelve!"=>"Tolv!", "Who stole it from me! Well, you tell him that Han Solo just stole back the Millennium Falcon for good."=>"Hvem stjal den fra mig! Nå, fortæller du ham at Han Solo blot stjal tilbage Millennium Falcon til gode.", "Who had it? Ducain?"=>"Der havde det? Ducain?", "Escape now, hug later."=>"Undslippe nu, knus senere.", "I used to be."=>"Jeg plejede at være.", "I've got a bad feeling about this."=>"Jeg har fået en dårlig fornemmelse om dette.", "Little bit more to it than that. You got a lot to learn."=>"Lidt mere til det end. Du fik en masse at lære.", "I know you do. That's why I'm giving it to you. Take it. You know how to use one of those?"=>"Jeg ved, du gør. Thats hvorfor jeg giver det til dig. Tage det. Du ved hvordan man bruger en af disse?", "You might need this."=>"Du måske har brug for dette.", "I used to wonder about that myself. Thought it was a bunch of mumbo-jumbo. A magical power holding together good and evil, the dark side and the light. Crazy thing is... it's true. The Force. The Jedi... All of it... It's all true."=>"Jeg plejede at undre sig over at jeg selv. Troede det var en flok mumbo-jumbo. En magisk magt holde sammen på godt og ondt, den mørke side og lys. Skøre ting er... det er sandt. Kraften. Jedi... Det hele... Det er sandt.", "A lot of rumors. Stories. People that knew him best think he went looking for the first Jedi temple."=>"En masse rygter. Historier. Mennesker, der kendte ham tror bedst han gik på udkig efter det første Jedi-templet.", "He was training a new generation of Jedi. One boy, an apprentice, turned against him, destroyed it all. Luke felt responsible. He just walked away from everything."=>"Han var at uddanne en ny generation af Jedi. En dreng, en lærling, vendte sig imod ham, ødelagt det hele. Luke følte sig ansvarlig. Han gik bare væk fra alting.", "This map's not complete. It's just a piece. Ever since Luke disappeared, people have been looking for him."=>"Dette kort er ikke komplet. Det er bare et stykke. Lige siden Luke forsvandt, har folk ledt efter ham.", "[stepping on board the Millennium Falcon] Chewie... we're home."=>"[stepping om bord på Millennium Falcon] Chewie... vi er hjemme.", "Jabba, you're a wonderful human being."=>"Jensen, du er et vidunderligt menneske.", "Fifteen, Jabba, and don't push it."=>"Femten, Jensen, og ikke skubbe det.", "Did you think I had a choice? But I got a nice easy charter now; I'll pay you back, plus a little extra. I just need a little more time."=>"Synes du jeg havde et valg? Men jeg fik en dejlig nem charter nu; Jeg vil betale dig tilbage, plus lidt ekstra. Jeg skal bare have lidt mere tid.", "Look, Jabba, even I get boarded sometimes."=>"Kig, Jensen, endda jeg får visiteret undertiden.", "Look, Jabba, next time you wanna talk to me, come see me yourself. Don't send one of these twerps."=>"Lede, Jensen, næste gang du ønsker at tale med mig, kom og se mig selv. Undlad at sende en af disse twerps.", "You didn't think I was gonna run, did you?"=>"Du syntes ikke jeg skulle køre, gjorde du?", "I've been waiting for you."=>"Jeg har ventet for dig.", "Right here, Jabba."=>"Lige her, Jensen.", "What?"=>"Hvad?", "That's your imagination."=>"Det er din fantasi.", "Sorry about the mess."=>"Ked af rod.", "Yes, I bet you have."=>"Ja, jeg vil vædde på du har.", "Over my dead body."=>"Over min døde krop.", "Even I get boarded sometimes. Do you think I have a choice."=>"Jeg får selv visiteret undertiden. Du tror, jeg har et valg.", "Tell Jabba..."=>"Fortælle Jabba...", "I don't have it WITH me."=>"Jeg har ikke det med mig.", "Yeah, but this time, I've got the money."=>"Ja, men denne gang, jeg har fået pengene.", "Tell Jabba that I've got his money."=>"Fortælle Jabba at jeg har fået sine penge.", "Yes, Greedo. As a matter of fact, I was just going to see your boss."=>"Ja, Greedo. Faktisk, jeg var lige til at se din chef.", "[slaps Luke's hand away] We're losing a deflector shield. Go strap yourselves in. I'm going to make the jump to light speed."=>"[klasker Lukes hånd væk] Vi taber en deflektor skjold. Gå strop jer i. Jeg har tænkt mig at tage springet til lysets hastighed.", "Traveling through hyperspace ain't like dusting crops, boy! Without precise calculations we could fly right through a star, or bounce too close to a supernova and that'd end your trip real quick, wouldn't it."=>"Rejser gennem hyperspace ain't som afstøvning afgrøder, dreng! Uden præcise beregninger vi kunne flyve lige igennem en stjerne eller hoppe for tæt på en supernova og der vil ende din tur virkelig hurtig, ville det.", "It'll take a few moments to get the coordinates from the navi-computer."=>"Det vil tage et par øjeblikke at få koordinaterne fra navi-computer.", "Here's where the fun begins."=>"Her er hvor sjovt begynder.", "Watch your mouth, kid, or you're gonna find yourself floating home! We'll be safe enough once we make the jump to hyperspace. Besides, I know a few maneuvers. We'll lose 'em."=>"Watch din mund, barn, eller du vil finde dig selv flydende hjem! Vi vil være sikker nok, når vi tage springet til hyperspace. Desuden, jeg kender et par manøvrer. Vi vil miste 'em.", "Stay sharp. There's two more coming in. They're gonna try and cut us off."=>"Bo skarpe. Der er to mere kommer i. They gonna prøve og afskære os.", "[sarcastic] Maybe you'd like it back in your cell, your Highness."=>"[sarkastisk] Måske ønsker du det tilbage i din celle, deres Højhed.", "Can't get out that way."=>"Kan ikke komme ud på den måde.", "[after Leia blasts a vent] What the hell are you doing?"=>"[efter Leia blaster en udluftningsanordning] Hvad fanden laver du?", "Sure hope the old man got that tractor beam out of commission, or this is gonna be a real short trip. Okay, hit it!"=>"Sikker håb den gamle mand fik denne traktor stråle ud af Kommissionen, eller det vil være en reel korte tur. Okay, hit det!", "I don't know, I can imagine quite a bit."=>"Jeg ikke ved, jeg kan forestille mig en hel del.", "[interested] Rich?"=>"[interesseret] Rige?", "Kid, I've flown from one side of this galaxy to the other, and I've seen a lot of strange stuff, but I've never seen *anything* to make me believe that there's one all-powerful Force controlling everything. 'Cause no mystical energy field controls *my* destiny. It's all a lot of simple tricks and nonsense."=>"Barn, jeg har fløjet fra den ene side af denne galakse til den anden, og jeg har set en masse mærkelige ting, men jeg har aldrig set * noget * at gøre mig til at tro, at der er en almægtig kraft kontrollerende alt. 'Cause nogen mystiske energifelt styrer * min * skæbne. Det er alle meget simple tricks og nonsens.", "Great shot, kid, that was one in a million!"=>"Stor skud, kid, der var en i en million!", "[indicating Luke] He's the brains, sweetheart!"=>"[der angiver Luke] Han er hjernen, kæreste!", "Good against remotes is one thing. Good against the living, that's something else."=>"God mod fjernbetjeninger er én ting. God mod de levende, som er noget andet.", "[sarcastically] Maybe you'd like it back in your cell, your highness."=>"[sarkastisk] Måske ønsker du det tilbage i din celle, deres Højhed.", "It's worse."=>"Det er værre.", "Absolutely, Your Worship. Look, I had everything under control until you led us down here! Now it's not going to take them long to figure out what happened to us."=>"Absolut, din gudstjeneste. Se, havde jeg alt under kontrol indtil du førte os ned her! Nu er det ikke vil tage dem lang tid at finde ud af hvad der skete for os.", "Garbage chute. Really wonderful idea. What an incredible smell you've discovered! Let's get out of here! Get away from there..."=>"Skrald sliske. Virkelig vidunderlig idé. Hvad en utrolig duft du har opdaget! Lad os komme ud af her! Komme væk fra der...", "What kept you?"=>"Hvad holdt du?", "One thing's for sure, we're all gonna be a lot thinner."=>"Én ting er sikkert, vi alle skal være meget tyndere.", "What's so important? What's he carrying?"=>"Hvad er så vigtigt? Hvad han bærer?", "Not this ship, sister."=>"Ikke dette skib, søster.", "Easy? You call that easy?"=>"Nem? Du kalde det nemt?", "You're all clear, kid, now let's *blow* this thing and go home!"=>"Du er alle klar, kid, nu lad os * slag * denne ting og gå hjem!", "YAHOOO!"=>"YAHOOO!", "And hope they don't have blasters."=>"Og håber, at de ikke har blasters.", "Yeah, great at getting us into trouble."=>"Ja, rigtig god til at få os ind i problemer.", "Where did you dig up that old fossil?"=>"Hvor du graver op den gamle fossile?", "Bring 'em on, I'd prefer a straight fight to all this sneaking around."=>"Bringer 'em, jeg ville foretrække en lige kamp til alle denne snigende rundt.", "Not a bad bit of rescuing, huh? You know, sometimes I amaze even myself."=>"Ikke en dårlig bit for redning, huh? Du ved, nogle gange jeg forbløffe selv mig selv.", "That's 'cause droids don't pull people's arms out of their sockets when they lose. Wookiees are known to do that."=>"Det er fordi droids ikke trække folks våben ud af deres sockets, når de taber. Wookiee er kendt for at gøre dette.", "Let him have it. It's not wise to upset a Wookiee."=>"Lad ham have det. Det er ikke klogt at forstyrre en Wookiee.", "What're you lookin' at? I know what I'm doin'."=>"Hvad er du Lookin' på? Jeg ved hvad jeg er doin'.", "Hey, Luke... may the Force be with you."=>"Hey, Luke... må kraften være med dig.", "What good's a reward if you ain't around to use it? Besides, attacking that battle station ain't my idea of courage. It's more like... suicide."=>"Hvad godt er en belønning, hvis du ikke er omkring at bruge det? Desuden angriber at slaget station er ikke min idé om modet. Det er mere som... selvmord.", "[baiting him] Still, she's got a lot of spirit. I don't know, whaddya think? You think a princess and a guy like me..."=>"[baiting ham] Stadig, har hun fået en masse ånd. Jeg ikke ved, whaddya tror? Du tror en prinsesse og en fyr som mig...", "I'm tryin' not to, kid."=>"Jeg Tryin' ikke til kid.", "It is for me, sister. Look, I ain't in this for your revolution, and I'm not in it for you, Princess. I expect to be well paid. I'm in it for the money."=>"Det er for mig, søster. Se, jeg er ikke i dette for din revolution, og jeg er ikke i det for dig, prinsesse. Jeg forventer at være godt betalt. Jeg er i det for pengene.", "Great, kid! Don't get cocky."=>"Stor, kid! Bliv ikke kæphøj.", "Nice! Come on."=>"Rar! Kom nu.", "No reward is worth this."=>"Ingen belønning er værd dette.", "Look, Your Worshipfulness, let's get one thing straight. I take orders from just one person: me."=>"Se, din Worshipfulness, lad os få én ting lige. Jeg tager ordrer fra blot én person: mig.", "I *did* say so before."=>"Jeg * gjorde * sige så før.", "This is *not* gonna work."=>"Det er * ikke * gonna arbejde.", "Get in there, you big furry oaf! I don't care what you smell!"=>"Få derinde, du store lodne oaf! Jeg er ligeglad hvad du lugter!", "Damn fool, I knew you were going to say that."=>"Damn fjols, jeg vidste du ville sige, at.", "I don't what we're gonna do now. Even if I could take off, I could never get past the tractor beam."=>"Jeg ved ikke hvad vi skal gøre nu. Selv om jeg kunne tage ud, kunne jeg aldrig komme forbi traktor stråle.", "Wonderful girl. Either I'm going to kill her or I'm beginning to like her."=>"Vidunderlige pige. Enten jeg har tænkt mig at dræbe hende, eller jeg begynder at kunne lide hende.", "She'll make point five past lightspeed. She may not look like much, but she's got it where it counts, kid. I've made a lot of special modifications myself."=>"Hun vil gøre punkt fem forbi lightspeed. Hun kan ikke ser ud af meget, men hun har fået det, hvor det tæller, kid. Jeg har lavet en masse specielle ændringer mig selv.", "[chuckles] What is it? Some kind of local trouble?"=>"[klukler] Hvad er det? Nogle slags lokale problemer?", "It's the ship that made the Kessel Run in less than twelve parsecs. I've outrun Imperial starships. Not the local bulk cruisers mind you, I'm talking about the big Corellian ships now. She's fast enough for you old man. What's the cargo?"=>"Det er det skib, der gjorde Kessel Kør i mindre end tolv Parsec. Jeg har løbe Imperial rumskibe. Ikke de lokale bulk krydstogtpassagerer mind dig, jeg taler om de store Corelliansk skibe nu. Hun er hurtig nok til du gamle mand. Hvad er lasten?", "Fast ship? You've never heard of the Millennium Falcon?"=>"Hurtig skib? Du har aldrig hørt om Millennium Falcon?", "I'm captain of the Millennium Falcon. Chewie here tells me you're lookin' for passage to the Alderaan system?"=>"Jeg er kaptajn på Millennium Falcon. Chewie her fortæller mig du er Lookin' for passage til Alderaan system?", "Hokey religions and ancient weapons are no match for a good blaster at your side, kid."=>"Hokey religioner og antikke våben er ingen match for en god blaster ved din side, kid.", "Don't everyone thank me at once."=>"Ikke alle takke mig på én gang.", "Well, you can forget your troubles with those Imperial slugs. I told you I'd outrun 'em."=>"Nå, kan du glemme din troubles med de kejserlige snegle. Jeg fortalte dig, jeg ville løbe 'em.", "Boring conversation anyway. LUKE, WE'RE GONNA HAVE COMPANY!"=>"Kedeligt samtale alligevel. LUKE, ER VI GONNA HAVE SELSKAB!", "Uh..."=>"Øh...", "Uh, uh... negative, negative. We had a reactor leak here now. Give us a few minutes to lock it down. Large leak, very dangerous."=>"Øh, øh... negativ, negativ. Vi havde en reaktor lække her nu. Giv os et par minutter til at låse den. Store lækage, meget farlige.", "[getting nervous] Uh, we had a slight weapons malfunction, but uh... everything's perfectly all right now. We're fine. We're all fine here now, thank you. How are you?"=>"[at få nervøs] Uh, vi havde en lille våben funktionsfejl, men øh... alt er perfekt alle lige nu. Vi er fint. Vi er alle fint her nu, tak. Hvordan går det?", "[sounding official] Uh, everything's under control. Situation normal."=>"[klingende officielle] Øh, er alt under kontrol. Situationen normale.", "Yeah, I'll bet you have."=>"Ja, jeg vil vædde på du har.", "Over my dead body!"=>"Over min døde krop!", "Even I get boarded sometimes. Do you think I had a choice?"=>"Jeg får selv visiteret undertiden. Tror du, jeg havde et valg?", "[stealthily going for his blaster] I don't have it with me. Tell Jabba..."=>"[listende går til hans blaster] Jeg har ikke det med mig. Fortælle Jabba...", "Yeah, but this time I've got the money."=>"Ja, men denne gang jeg har fået pengene.", "Yes, Greedo. I was just going to see your boss. Tell Jabba I've got his money."=>"Ja, Greedo. Jeg var lige til at se din chef. Fortælle Jabba jeg har fået sine penge.", "What're you looking at? I know what I'm doing."=>"Hvad kigger du på? Jeg ved, hvad jeg gør.", "[as Luke walks away] Hey, Luke. May the Force be with you."=>"[som Luke går væk] Hey, Luke. Kraften kan være med dig.", "What good is a reward if you ain't around to use it? Besides, attacking that battle station is not my idea of courage. It's more like, suicide."=>"Hvad artig er en belønning, hvis du ikke er omkring at bruge det? Desuden er angriber at slaget station ikke min idé om modet. Det er mere som selvmord.", "That's right, yeah. Got some old debts I gotta pay off with this stuff. Even if I didn't, you don't think I'd be fool enough to stick around here, do you? Why don't you come with us? You're pretty good in a fight. We could use you."=>"Det er rigtigt, ja. Fik nogle gamle gæld jeg gotta afbetale med denne ting. Selvom jeg ikke gjorde det, tror du ikke jeg ville være fjols nok til at holde sig omkring her, gør du? Hvorfor ikke du kommer med os? Du er temmelig god i en kamp. Vi kan bruge dig.", "I'll get him!"=>"Jeg får ham!", "Look out he's loose!"=>"Se han er løs!", "Better her than me!"=>"Bedre hende end mig!", "Marching into a detention area is not what I had in mind."=>"Marcherende i en tilbageholdelse område er ikke, hvad jeg havde i tankerne.", "I use them for smuggling. I never thought I'd be smuggling myself in them. This is ridiculous."=>"Jeg bruger dem for smugling. Jeg troede aldrig jeg ville smugling dem selv. Dette er latterligt." }.freeze
